section.def:
Chairman
                (主席) means the Chairman of the Board appointed
            under section 3(2)(a)(i) or any other person when acting as Chairman;

employer
                (僱主) has the same meaning as in section
                2(1) of the Employment Ordinance (Cap. 57);

Fund
                (基金) means the Employees Retraining Fund
            established under section 6;

levy
                (徵款) means the levy imposed under section
                14(1);

quota
                (配額) means a quota allocated under section
                14(4);

visa
                (簽證) means a visa issued under section
                61 of the Immigration Ordinance (Cap. 115);

paragraph.content:
to determine matters relating to the remuneration and terms and
                        conditions of appointment or employment of the employees of the
                        Board;
